prompt_text:
Analyze the location details. Return ONLY a valid JSON object as described, with no surrounding text or markdown:
{
  "market": {
    "tech_presence": "Industry presence details",
    "major_employers": ["List of major employers"],
    "area_type": "Business district type"
  },
  "economic": {
    "cost_of_living": "Cost of living details",
    "salary_competitiveness": "Salary market position"
  },
  "environment": {
    "commute": "Transportation analysis",
    "work_model": "Remote/hybrid trends",
    "amenities": ["List of key amenities"]
  }
}

Extract and analyze the compensation and benefits information. Return ONLY a valid JSON object as described, with no surrounding text or markdown:
{
 "salary_range": {"min": "Minimum salary", "max": "Maximum salary", "currency": "Currency", "period": "Hourly/Annual"},
 "benefits": ["List of key benefits"]
}

Analyze required skills. Return ONLY a valid JSON object as described, no explanation or other text:
{
  "technical": {
    "required": ["List of required technical skills"],
    "preferred": ["List of preferred technical skills"],
    "certifications": ["Required certifications"]
  },
  "soft_skills": ["List of required soft skills"]
}

List the specific tools, technologies, platforms, and frameworks mentioned in the job description. Return ONLY a valid JSON object with this structure, no explanation or other text:
{
  "tools": ["List of required tools/technologies"]
}

Analyze opportunities for professional development and career growth mentioned in the job posting. Return ONLY a valid JSON object with this structure, no explanation or other text:
{
 "development_paths": ["Suggested learning paths"],
 "growth_opportunities": ["Career growth paths"]
}

Analyze the company information provided or implied. Return ONLY a valid JSON object as described, no explanation or other text:
{
  "overview": {
    "size": "Company size",
    "industry": "Industry focus",
    "stage": "Company stage/maturity"
  },
  "culture": {
    "values": ["Company values"],
    "environment": "Work environment"
  },
   "growth_trajectory": "Company growth outlook"
}

Analyze the following resume text. Return ONLY a valid JSON object with this exact structure, no explanation or other text:
{
  "professional_summary": "Brief overview of candidate's profile",
  "contact": {
    "name": "Full name",
    "email": "Email address",
    "phone": "Phone number",
    "location": "City, State"
  },
  "experience": [
    {
      "title": "Job title",
      "company": "Company name",
      "location": "Location",
      "dates": "Employment dates",
      "highlights": ["Key achievements and responsibilities"]
    }
  ],
  "education": [
    {
      "degree": "Degree name",
      "institution": "School name",
      "location": "Location",
      "graduation_date": "Date"
    }
  ],
  "skills": {
    "technical": ["List of technical skills"],
    "soft_skills": ["List of soft skills"]
  },
  "certifications": ["List of certifications"],
  "clearance": "Security clearance level if mentioned"
}

Compare the provided Resume Analysis (JSON) with the Job Analysis (JSON) and return ONLY a valid JSON object with this exact structure:
{
  "overall_match_score": 85,
  "detailed_scores": {
    "skills_match": 90,
    "experience_match": 85,
    "education_match": 80,
    "clearance_match": 100
  },
  "strengths": [
    "Detailed strength points that align with job requirements"
  ],
  "gaps": [
    "Specific areas where the candidate could improve"
  ],
  "recommendations": "Detailed, actionable recommendations for the candidate to improve their match"
}
